## Research Context (read before making design decisions)
All verified research lives in `.context/research/`:
- `owasp-llm-top10.md` — OWASP coverage gaps mapped to our scanners
- `competitor-scanners.md` — LLM Guard 35 scanners vs our 6, what's worth adding
- `server-architecture-patterns.md` — auth/caching/batching from vLLM, TGI, Ollama
- `models-and-datasets.md` — classifier options + dataset sizes/licenses
- `openai-privacy-filter.md` — 50M-param PII model, integration plan
- `api-contract.md` — v1/v2 endpoint specs
- `adoption-and-distribution.md` — distribution strategy
Also read: `.context/design-next-phase.md` (synthesized design doc with all decisions)

